&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;When a law firm needs an attorney in a courtroom on short notice,&amp;nbsp;Docketly&amp;nbsp;delivers, and&amp;nbsp;you&#39;re&amp;nbsp;the person who makes that happen.&amp;nbsp;As an Operations Associate on our Coverage team, you own a live book of court hearings and&amp;nbsp;work&amp;nbsp;the phones, texts, and email to lock in attorney coverage before the clock runs out.&amp;nbsp;The job is part dispatcher, part closer, part account manager:&amp;nbsp;fast, measurable, and never boring.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
